or-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">门店价</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">门市价</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">（如品牌专柜标价、商品吊牌价</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">、厂商指导价</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">、厂商建议零售价、实体门店指导价</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">、实体门店展示销售价等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">）等某一价格基础上计算出的优惠比例或优惠金额</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">；如有疑问</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">，您可在购买前联系商户</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">猛戳客服进行咨询</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '29');
INSERT INTO `about_us` VALUES ('28', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">总则</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">为保障餐饮安全，构建起猛戳</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">APP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">餐饮业务的食品安全保护网，猛戳秉承“消费者第一”的理念，依据《中华人民共和国食品安全法》、、《网络餐饮服务食品安全监督管理办法》、《网络食品安全违法行为查处办法》、《中华人民共和国消费者权益保护法》等法律法规规定，制定《猛戳餐饮安全管理办法》。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">猛戳餐饮安全管理的原则和目标是，确保餐饮安全风险商户零漏报、餐饮安全高危商户零容忍、餐饮安全零事故；同时与社会各界广泛合作、共同治理，成为食品安全产业发展的有益推动者。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">此管理办法的适用范围是，以猛戳平台为载体开展的网络餐饮服务，具体指猛戳餐饮商户通过猛戳平台接受消费者订餐需求后制作并提供餐品的餐饮经营活动。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">第一章</span> </b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">入网餐饮商户资质核查</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">（一）入网前资质核查</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">请商户提供符合当地法律法规要求的有效证照资质原件，并结合商户实际情况核对许可证日期、地址、经营范围等内容；自入驻商户上传符合上述要求的有效证照。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">5. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">品控部门依据当地法律法规规定，对上传的商户证照资质信息进行验证，确保真实、有效。经品控严格审核通过的商户，才能够上线。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">（二）入网后定期核验</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">6. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">通过猛戳研发的“商户证照云审核系统”对一证多用、证照过期、证照造假和仿冒、超出经营范围等情况进行定期重点核查，发现问题第一时间通知整改，情况严重时对商户做下线处理。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">7. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">实行第三方专业机构“神秘客抽检”制度，定期对商户环境及证照进行抽检，出现不达标情况将督促整改，情况严重时对商户做下线处理。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">（三）定期上报与沟通机制</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">8. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">定期将猛戳平台证照不合规的餐饮商户向政府监管部门上报，将信息向行业共享，实现信息互联互通。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">第二章</span> </b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">商户信息建档与展示</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">（一）商户信息建档</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">9. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">商户入网前，猛戳与商户签订入驻协议，并与商户明确商户食品安全管理人员，与双方食品安全管理责任。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">10. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">商户入网后，责任人记录商户负责人的姓名、身份证信息、联系电话、商户地址等信息，并录入系统；</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">自入驻商户在后台自行提交上述信息。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">11. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">商户入网后，形成独立的商户档案信息系统，涵盖入网时录入的基础信息，及商户入网、置休、下线等行为变化，餐饮安全量化分级的评级情况，消费者餐饮安全投诉及评价信息等，供公司内部管理与外部监管部门调阅。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">（二）商户信息变更</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">12. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">如有证照更换、经营人变更、地址变更等情况，商户尽快在后台更新以上信息。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">13. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">责任人定期巡店，发现证照过期、经营人更换、地址变更等情况，立刻在后台更新商户信息，提交总部审核，情况严重时可对商户做下线处理。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">（三）商户信息展示</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">14. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">猛戳商户经营页面亮出餐饮商户营业执照，按照法律规定应该取得食品经营许可证的商户，还应该亮出食品经营许可证。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">15. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">鼓励商户在猛戳平台向用户展示店面和厨房环境，公示原材料和消毒清洁标准及相应供应商资质；对于有效展示真实信息的商户，猛戳将给予商户更好的展示位置。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">第三章</span> </b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">商户退出</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">16. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">如商户提供给平台或对用户公示的信息存在虚假不实的情况，被查到后应立即改正，情况严重时将对商户做下线处理，永久不合作</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">17. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">如商户因餐饮安全问题被立案侦查、处以刑罚、被公安拘留、被吊销许可证或停业等，猛戳将立即将商户下线。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">18. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">如通过媒体报道、猛戳用户投诉及评价数据监控等方式发现商户重大餐饮安全侵害行为，猛戳将立即将商户下线，并永不进行合作。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">第四章</span> </b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">消费者保障</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">（一）餐饮安全信息提供</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">19. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">在猛戳平台商户页面展示商户“餐饮安全量化分级动态指标”，亮出商户证照信息，确保消费者对商户餐饮安全情况了解知悉。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">（二）餐饮安全举报与投诉处理</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">20. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">消费者可通过猛戳</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> APP </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">在线客服的餐饮安全专用入口及客服投诉热线，进行餐饮安全的投诉与举报。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">21. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">客服部门成立专门的餐饮安全投诉应对小组，建立餐饮安全投诉等级制度，不同等级餐饮安全投诉由不同专业等级客服应对解决。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">22. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">所有餐饮安全相关投诉，确保</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 24 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">小时内有解决方案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">23. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">用户在猛戳消费，一旦出现餐品里有违规食品添加剂、异物、或出现用户因菜品质量就医等问题，用户提交信息后，商家需无条件向用户进行有效协商或赔付。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">（三）餐饮安全宣传</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">24. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">在特定季节、节日等时期通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> APP </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">对消费者进行餐饮安全提示，如夏天提示少选择冷食，餐品送到及时食用等等。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">第五章</span> </b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">组织保障</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">25. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">成立食品安全领导小组，设立首席食品安全官，筹划和组建食品安全管理工作组织体系，组建食品安全团队及各业务及其职能部门开展工作。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">26. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">餐饮平台业务部门及相关职能部门，以本规则为指导制定本部门餐饮安全制度，并与员工绩效挂钩。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">27. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">对餐饮安全事故进行分类分级，明确不同类别和等级餐饮安全事故的责任归属和处罚方式。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">第六章</span> </b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">社会共治</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">28. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-latin\">猛戳将挖掘餐饮安全方面的用户评价、投诉和举报数据，进行深度分析，形成智能数据报告，作为餐饮安全自查依据。在此过程中，发现违法行为及时制止，并将平台商户餐饮安全情况定期向政府监管部门报送。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">29. </span>